         <abstract id="aspace_6177f01fb8cb518ab2bcf418f0570385">Letters and diaries document Long's YMCA work in Tientsin and Mukden and shed light on the political situation in China during the 1920s. Austin O. Long was a YMCA worker in Tientsin, China from 1919 to 1923 and in Mukden, Manchuria from 1924 to 1928.</abstract>
